Prepare IMPACT annotations

Source: R/IMPACT.R
IMPACT.postprocess_annotations.Rd

Transform IMPACT annotations from wide format (one row per SNP) to long format (multiple rows per SNP).

IMPACT.postprocess_annotations(ANNOT_MELT, order_loci = T, no_no_loci = NULL)
